text: Wang Dou (born 18 May 1993) is a Chinese hurdler who specializes in the 100 m distance. She who a bronze medal at the 2017 Asian Championships and placed fourth at the 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:Chinese female hurdlers Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for China
